(49, 'Phần 2: Cú pháp &amp;amp; Biến', 'phan-2-cu-phap-bien', '', 'active', 'Phase 1: PHP Basics', 2, '<div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0 \"><!-- Breadcrumbs -->\r\n<div class=\"mb-6 sm:mb-8\"><!-- Control Structures -->\r\n<div style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[48px] font-bold text-home-heading leading-tight sm:leading-snug md:leading-[60px] lg:leading-[64px] text-start mb-3 sm:mb-4\" style=\"font-family: \'Space Grotesk\', sans-serif;\">Control Structures</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\" style=\"font-family: \'Plus Jakarta Sans\', sans-serif;\">Master if/else statements, switch cases, and conditional logic in PHP.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Arrays & Loops -->\r\n<div style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[48px] font-bold text-home-heading leading-tight sm:leading-snug md:leading-[60px] lg:leading-[64px] text-start mb-3 sm:mb-4\" style=\"font-family: \'Space Grotesk\', sans-serif;\">Arrays &amp; Loops</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\" style=\"font-family: \'Plus Jakarta Sans\', sans-serif;\">Work with arrays and iterate through data using loops in PHP.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Functions -->\r\n<div style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[48px] font-bold text-home-heading leading-tight sm:leading-snug md:leading-[60px] lg:leading-[64px] text-start mb-3 sm:mb-4\" style=\"font-family: \'Space Grotesk\', sans-serif;\">Functions</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\" style=\"font-family: \'Plus Jakarta Sans\', sans-serif;\">Create reusable code blocks with PHP functions and understand scope.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Content Sections -->\r\n<div class=\"space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 mb-8 sm:mb-12\"><!-- Installation & Setup Content -->\r\n<div style=\"display: none;\"><!-- What you will learn Section -->\r\n<div class=\"p-4 sm:p-6\">\r\n<h2 class=\"font-space text-3xl  font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6\">Coming Soon</h2>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-plus\">Content for Control Structures will be available soon.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Syntax & Variables Content -->\r\n<div><!-- What you will learn Section -->\r\n<div class=\"rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden mb-12 bg-white\" style=\"box-shadow: 0 2.667px 8px 0 rgba(43, 140, 238, 0.05);\">\r\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-start gap-6 p-6 self-stretch\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\r\n<h2 class=\"text-base font-medium leading-6 text-gray-900\" style=\"font-family: \'Plus Jakarta Sans\', sans-serif;\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" title=\"frame-238.png\" src=\"https://laragon.net/content/uploads/2026/03/28/frame-238.png\" alt=\"frame-238.png\"></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-3\">\r\n<li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-home-accent mt-2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<span class=\"text-sm text-home-body leading-[22px]\"> Understand PHP tags &lt;?php ?&gt; </span></li>\r\n<li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-home-accent mt-2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<span class=\"text-sm text-home-body leading-[22px]\"> Datatypes: String, Integer, Array </span></li>\r\n<li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-home-accent mt-2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<span class=\"text-sm text-home-body leading-[22px]\"> Declare and use variables </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Implementation Guide Section -->\r\n<div class=\"rounded-home-lg overflow-hidden mb-12 sm:mb-24\">\r\n<div class=\"\">\r\n<h2 class=\"font-plus text-3xl sm:text-[36px]  font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3\">Implementation Guide</h2>\r\n<p class=\"sm:text-xl  text-md text-gray-600 leading-[22px] mb-8 font-plus\">Learn how to write your first PHP script and store data in variables.</p>\r\n<!-- Steps -->\r\n<div class=\"space-y-8 sm:space-y-12\"><!-- Step 1 -->\r\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#F3F4F6] px-6 py-4\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" title=\"arrow-big-right.png\" src=\"https://laragon.net/content/uploads/2026/03/28/arrow-big-right.png\" alt=\"arrow-big-right.png\">\r\n<h3 class=\"font-space text-md font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2\">Step 1: Create a PHP file</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\" rounded-[12px] bg-white shadow-[0_2.667px_8px_0_rgba(43,140,238,0.05)] flex flex-col items-start gap-6 py-6 self-stretch\">\r\n<p class=\"text-sm px-6 gap-2 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-plus font-normal\">Create \'index.php\' in \'C:/laragon/www/team-php/\'</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Step 2 -->\r\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#F3F4F6] px-6 py-4\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" title=\"arrow-big-right.png\" src=\"https://laragon.net/content/uploads/2026/03/28/arrow-big-right.png\" alt=\"arrow-big-right.png\">\r\n<h3 class=\"font-space text-md font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2\">Step 2: Write code</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\" rounded-[12px] bg-white shadow-[0_2.667px_8px_0_rgba(43,140,238,0.05)] flex flex-col items-start px-6 gap-6 py-6 self-stretch\">\r\n<div class=\"bg-[#1E293B]  rounded-[12px] p-4 sm:p-6 overflow-x-auto w-full\">\r\n<pre class=\"text-xs font-plus font-semibold  text-[#D4D4D4] font-mono\"><code>&lt;?php\r\n    $greeting = \"Hello, Laragon!\";\r\n    $year = 2025;\r\n    echo $greeting . \" Welcome to \" . $year;\r\n    ?&gt;</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Step 3 -->\r\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#F3F4F6] px-6 py-4\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" title=\"arrow-big-right.png\" src=\"https://laragon.net/content/uploads/2026/03/28/arrow-big-right.png\" alt=\"arrow-big-right.png\">\r\n<h3 class=\"font-space text-md font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2\">Step 3: Run it</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\" rounded-[12px] bg-white shadow-[0_2.667px_8px_0_rgba(43,140,238,0.15)] flex flex-col items-start gap-6 py-6 self-stretch\">\r\n<p class=\"text-sm px-6 gap-2 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-plus font-normal\">Open browser: http://learn-php.test</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Common Issues Section -->\r\n<div class=\"rounded-home-lg overflow-hidden\">\r\n<div class=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" title=\"bug.png\" src=\"https://laragon.net/content/uploads/2026/03/28/bug.png\" alt=\"bug.png\">\r\n<h2 class=\"font-plus text-3xl sm:text-[36px]  font-medium text-home-heading mb-3\">Common Issues</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"sm:text-xl  text-md text-gray-600 leading-[22px] mb-4 sm:mb-6 font-plus\">Learn how to write your first PHP script and store data in variables.</p>\r\n<!-- Issues List -->\r\n<div class=\"space-y-8 sm:space-y-12\"><!-- Issue 1 -->\r\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#FEF2F2] px-6 py-4\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" title=\"info.png\" src=\"https://laragon.net/content/uploads/2026/03/28/info.png\" alt=\"info.png\">\r\n<h3 class=\"text-base font-medium text-home-heading leading-6 mb-2\" style=\"font-family: \'Plus Jakarta Sans\', sans-serif;\">White screen / 500 Error</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\" rounded-[12px] bg-white shadow-[0_2.667px_8px_0_rgba(43,140,238,0.15)] flex flex-col items-start gap-6 py-6 self-stretch\">\r\n<p class=\"text-sm font-normal text-[#DB3D23] leading-[22px] px-6\" style=\"font-family: \'Plus Jakarta Sans\', sans-serif;\">Check for missing semicolons (;) at end of lines.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Issue 2 -->\r\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#FEF2F2] px-6 py-4\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" title=\"info.png\" src=\"https://laragon.net/content/uploads/2026/03/28/info.png\" alt=\"info.png\">\r\n<h3 class=\"text-base font-medium text-home-heading leading-6 mb-2\" style=\"font-family: \'Plus Jakarta Sans\', sans-serif;\">Variables not showing</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\" rounded-[12px] bg-white shadow-[0_2.667px_8px_0_rgba(43,140,238,0.15)] flex flex-col items-start gap-6 py-6 self-stretch\">\r\n<p class=\"text-sm font-normal text-[#DB3D23] leading-[22px] px-6\" style=\"font-family: \'Plus Jakarta Sans\', sans-serif;\">Ensure you use the $ sign before variable names.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'PHP Basics Tutorial', 'Learn PHP basics step by step', '2026-03-28 10:56:34', '2026-04-01 10:22:17', 'Học cách viết script PHP đầu tiên và lưu trữ dữ liệu vào biến', 'tutorial', 0, 0, 0.00),
(50, 'Phần 1: Cài đặt &amp;amp; Thiết lập', 'phan-1-cai-dat-thiet-lap', '', 'active', 'Phase 1: PHP Basics', 1, '<h1>Working with Forms</h1>\r\n<p>Forms help collect user input from browsers.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>GET vs POST</li>\r\n<li>Validation</li>\r\n<li>Security</li>\r\n</ul>', 'PHP Forms Guide', 'Handle forms in PHP', '2026-03-28 10:56:34', '2026-04-01 10:20:52', 'Bắt đầu với việc thiết lập môi trường phát triển PHP bằng Laragon', 'tutorial', 0, 0, 0.00),
